-- Date: 2026-07-15
-- Purpose: U-B.4 backfill output — the config_components / config_resources /
--   config_events / migration_backfill_state rows produced by backfill.php
--   run 'run-20260715-final-ub4' against a replica of the 2026-07-15 09:51
--   production dump (owner has no PHP CLI on the server, so the rows ship as
--   SQL). RUN 2026_07_15_001 FIRST — these rows were extracted from the
--   repaired JSON that seeder creates.
-- Affected tables: config_components, config_resources, config_events,
--   migration_backfill_state, server_configurations (revision only).
