-- Safety: all ids offset by +10000 (never collides with rows live dual-write
--   creates); every INSERT is IGNORE + guarded per config — if a config has
--   ANY non-backfill config_events row (live dual-write touched it since the
--   dump), that config's entire block no-ops (dual-write self-materializes
--   its rows). revision UPDATEs are guarded on the pre-backfill value.
-- Idempotent: yes (fixed ids + INSERT IGNORE + guarded UPDATEs).
-- ============================================================================

